      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 52.1 - 老子 52.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 52.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天下有始，以為天下母。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(The Dao) which originated all under the sky is to be considered as the mother of them all.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-052__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-052</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 52.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 52.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>〉既得其母，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When the mother is found, we know what her children should be.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-052__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-052</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 52.4 - 老子 52.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 52.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>以知其子，既知其子，復守其母，沒身不殆。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When one knows that he is his mother's child, and proceeds to guard (the qualities of) the mother that belong to him, to the end of his life he will be free from all peril.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-052__align-004">
