      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 52.14 - 老子 52.16</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 52.6 - 老子 52.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>見小曰明，守柔曰強。用其光，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The perception of what is small is (the secret of clear- sightedness; the guarding of what is soft and tender is (the secret of) strength.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
